   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "Thirty percent of deployed systems were never fully accepted: customers would sign, we’d deploy, and six months later, it came back. We were sending teams to uninstall while trying to hit revenue targets."
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.themanufacturer.com/articles/30-iot-projects-fail-proof-concept-stage/",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "Decision-makers believe that 30% of their company’s revenue two years from now will come from the Internet of Things, yet almost a third of projects aren’t moving beyond the initial phase."
  },
  {
   "url": "https://newsroom.cisco.com/c/r/newsroom/en/us/a/y2017/m05/cisco-survey-reveals-close-to-three-fourths-of-iot-projects-are-failing.html",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "60 percent of IoT initiatives stall at the Proof of Concept (PoC) stage and only 26 percent of companies have had an IoT initiative that they considered a complete success. Even worse: a third of all completed projects were not considered a success."
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.einpresswire.com/article/814264810/inova-rpdu-solutions-see-successful-pilot-deployments-to-power-the-ai-era",
   "stance": "contradicts",
   "quote": "Inova, a leading innovator in data center infrastructure solutions, is proud to announce the successful pilot deployment of its next-generation rack PDU(rPDU) solutions across several client sites. Early results show strong performance"
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.casestudies.com/company/sunbird-dcim/case-study/sunbirds-dcim-energy-and-environmental-monitoring-is-just-the-start-for-f5s-product-development-lab",
   "stance": "contradicts",
   "quote": "Sunbird DCIM deployed PIQ across all 118 racks and integrated with Raritan iPDUs and more than 100 temperature/humidity sensors, giving F5 continuous power and thermal visibility."
  }
 ]
}

